purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes for laboratory test panel names associated with detecting the presence of viral hemorrhagic fever nucleic acid.),(Data Element Scope: Laboratory tests names that were ordered or observed.),(Inclusion Criteria: component: viral hemorrhagic fever nucleic acid (panel tests);  

LOINC Search terms: “(filovirus or ebola or marburg or arenavirus or lassa or lujo or junin or sabia or machupo or guanarito or crimean) nucleic -(culture or isolate or panel)”;  

Include tests for viruses listed in "Note";),(Exclusion Criteria: none)
